snippet.title: Fugue Trailer 01
snippet.description:
Make music, chimes, and melodies as you try and solve each level in this mathematical puzzle game. Take your name, relax, and get birds to their nest with matching numbers. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/870400/Fugue/
